  "subject": "[SO][SDNC] Configure RFC 8040 APIs to support new SDNC version",
  "commit_message": "[SO][SDNC] Configure RFC 8040 APIs to support new SDNC version\n\nUpdate component configuration files to use new restconf API\ninstead of unsupported Biermann API.\nFiles in the following components are updated:\n- SDNC\n- SO\n- OOF\n- Policy\n\nIssue-ID: OOM-3259\n\nChange-Id: I4f52feb1a86b2470b05f981184e5f10468a93f98\nSigned-off-by: Andreas Geissler <andreas-geissler@telekom.de>\n",
